---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro'
import { withBase } from '../../utils/base'
---

<DocsLayout title="Pack Documentation" description="Pack is an ultra-fast Ruby package manager written in Rust.">
  <a slot="sidebar" href={withBase('/docs/')} class="sidebar-home">Documentation</a>
  <nav class="sidebar-nav">
    <p class="sidebar-section">Getting Started</p>
    <a href={withBase('/docs/getting-started')}>Introduction</a>
    <a href={withBase('/docs/installation')}>Installation</a>
    <a href={withBase('/docs/quick-start')}>Quick Start</a>
    <p class="sidebar-section">Commands</p>
    <a href={withBase('/docs/commands')}>All Commands</a>
    <a href={withBase('/docs/commands#install')}>pack install</a>
    <a href={withBase('/docs/commands#gem')}>pack gem</a>
    <a href={withBase('/docs/commands#exec')}>pack exec</a>
    <a href={withBase('/docs/commands#rails')}>pack rails</a>
    <p class="sidebar-section">Guides</p>
    <a href={withBase('/docs/rails')}>Rails Support</a>
    <a href={withBase('/docs/docker')}>Docker & Pack</a>
    <a href={withBase('/docs/plugins')}>Plugin System</a>
  </nav>

  <div class="doc-content">
    <h1>Introduction</h1>
    <p class="lead">Pack is an ultra-fast Ruby package manager written in Rust.</p>

    <h2>Why Pack?</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>157,000x faster</strong> — Gemfile parsing in microseconds vs milliseconds</li>
      <li><strong>No Ruby required</strong> — Works on systems without Ruby installed</li>
      <li><strong>Native gem support</strong> — Direct RubyGems.org integration</li>
      <li><strong>First-class Rails</strong> — Commands designed for Rails developers</li>
      <li><strong>Binary lockfile</strong> — pack.lock with MessagePack for instant parsing</li>
      <li><strong>Parallel downloads</strong> — Uses Rayon for concurrent gem installs</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Quick Example</h2>
    <pre><code>$ pack install
Installing 47 gems... <span class="success">done</span> in 2.3s

$ pack server
Pack v0.1.0 — Rails 8.0.0
<span class="success">Server running on http://localhost:3000</span></code></pre>

    <h2>Installation</h2>
    <pre><code>cargo install pack</code></pre>
    <p>Or download a pre-built binary from the releases page.</p>

    <h2>Next Steps</h2>
    <p>
      <a href={withBase('/docs/getting-started')}>Get started with Pack →</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
  .sidebar-home {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--fg);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
    display: block;
  }

  .sidebar-nav {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--sp-1);
  }

  .sidebar-section {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-top: var(--sp-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-2);
  }

  .sidebar-nav a {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--fg-secondary);
    padding: var(--sp-1) 0;
    transition: color var(--duration) var(--ease);
  }

  .sidebar-nav a:hover { color: var(--fg); }

  .doc-content {
    padding: var(--sp-8) var(--sp-10);
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .doc-content h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
  }

  .doc-content h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-top: var(--sp-8);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
    padding-top: var(--sp-6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .doc-content .lead {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--fg-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-8);
  }

  .doc-content p {
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .doc-content ul {
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
    padding-left: var(--sp-6);
  }

  .doc-content li {
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-2);
  }

  .doc-content pre {
    background: var(--bg-muted);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: var(--sp-4);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-6);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .doc-content code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    background: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .doc-content pre code {
    color: var(--fg);
  }

  .doc-content .success { color: var(--green); }

  .doc-content a {
    color: var(--accent);
  }
</style>
